00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:16,020
Looks like that person badly needs some hand cream.

411
00:24:16,020 --> 00:24:20,060
But whatever we want to conclude about that, the mites view, it is really different from

412
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:21,260
our view.

413
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:23,980
Even though again, we're talking about the shape.

414
00:24:23,980 --> 00:24:26,260
We're talking about the extension of it.

415
00:24:26,260 --> 00:24:31,620
We're talking about things that ought to be among the primary qualities.

416
00:24:31,620 --> 00:24:34,460
But perceptions vary.

417
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,060
Among species, yes.

418
00:24:36,060 --> 00:24:37,740
But even for us.

419
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:43,060
Phylonus, one of the characters in the dialogue here, says, from what you've laid down, it

