00:25:22,300 --> 00:25:24,300
by us that's in the thing.

433
00:25:24,300 --> 00:25:28,740
We've got to say, if we really take that to correspond, in both cases, that they're

434
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:29,740
both in the thing.

435
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:32,140
But that's a manifest contradiction.

436
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:36,620
Well, it's not just a question of different species.

437
00:25:36,620 --> 00:25:40,060
Maybe we want to say, I don't care how a mite sees things, or how an elephant would

